## Essential Wireshark Filters

```bash
# Basic FTP traffic
ftp

# Successful logins
ftp.response.code == 230

# Failed logins
ftp.response.code == 530

# Username attempts
ftp.request.command == "USER"

# Password attempts
ftp.request.command == "PASS"

# File transfers
ftp.request.command == "RETR" or ftp.request.command == "STOR"

# Brute force detection (multiple failures)
ftp.response.code == 530
# Then: Statistics → Conversations
```

